
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>incio de sesion</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>


<body class="m-5">
    <div class="m-5 bg-light rounded text-center border border-primary">
        <h2 class="fs-1">♠ Pagina de registro ♠</h2>
        <p class="fs-5">
            Introduce tus apellidos.
        </p>
        <input type="text" class="rounded fs-5 text-center border border-dark" placeholder="Introduce tus apellidos"> 
        <p class="fs-5">
            Introduce tus nombres.
        </p>
        <input type="text" class="rounded fs-5 text-center border border-dark" placeholder="Introduce tus nombres"> 
        <br>
        <p class="fs-5">Ingresa tu correo electronico:</p>
        <input type="email" class="rounded fs-5 text-center border border-dark" placeholder="Correo electronoco">
        <p class="fs-5">
            Marca tu fecha de nacimiento para autorizar el registro.
        </p>
        <input type="date" class="rounded fs-5 text-center border border-dark" min="1950-12-31" max="2022-12-31">
        <p class="fs-5"> 
            Ingrese su numero de telefono para guardar tu informacion.
        </p>
        <input type="text" class="rounded fs-5 text-center border border-dark" placeholder="Introdusca su numero de telefono">
        <p class="fs-5">
            Introduce una contraseña de registro.
        </p>
        <input type="password" class="rounded fs-5 text-center border border-dark" minlength="10" maxlength="10" placeholder="Introduce tu contraseña">
        <br>
        <br>
        <button href="" class="btn btn-danger">Capturar registro</button>

        <br>
        <br>
    </div>
</body>
</html>